===Etymology===
From [[Old Church Slavonic|OCS]] '''домови''' (“to the house”), the [[dative case|dative]] singular of [[домъ|дом]].

===Adverb===
'''домой''' (domój)

#[[home]], [[homewards]], to the [[house]]
#:*{{RUchar|[[я|Мне]] [[пора|пора́]] домо́й}} — ''It’s time for me to go home.''

